snippet.title: MARVEL SNAP is Now on PC | OFFICIAL PC LAUNCH TRAILER
snippet.description:
Go wide or go home, MARVEL SNAP is officially launched on PC!! Head to Steam to cruise the Marvel Multiverse—now in horizontal style 

Don't miss a thing, follow MARVEL SNAP on social and join the MARVEL SNAP community!

► Watch Marvel on Disney+: https://bit.ly/2XyBSIW
► Subscribe to Marvel on YouTube: http://bit.ly/WeO3YJ
